<section class="rules-combined">
<h2>Regelkarten</h2>
<div class="rc-grid">

<div class="rc-card c-amber">
<div class="rc-card-topbar"></div>
<div class="rc-card-body">
<div class="rc-card-label">📚 Countable / Uncountable</div>
<div class="rc-card-num">1</div>
<div class="rc-rule">Manche Nomen kann man <b>zählen</b> (countable), andere <b>nicht</b> (uncountable).</div>
<div class="rc-examples-new">
<b>countable</b> (haben einen Plural):<br>
<i>one apple → two apples</i><br>
<i>book, car, tomato, friend …</i><br><br>
<b>uncountable</b> (kein Plural):<br>
<i>cheese, fruit, music, love</i><br>
<i>water, milk, bread, sugar …</i>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="rc-card c-green">
<div class="rc-card-topbar"></div>
<div class="rc-card-body">
<div class="rc-card-label">✅ Bejahter Satz</div>
<div class="rc-card-num">2</div>
<div class="rc-rule">In <b>bejahten Sätzen</b> nimmst du immer <b>a lot of</b> – egal ob countable oder uncountable.</div>
<div class="rc-formula">
  <span class="fc fc-subj">Subjekt</span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">+</span><span class="fc fc-verb">Verb</span></span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">+</span><span class="fc fc-alot">a lot of</span></span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">+</span><span class="fc fc-do">Nomen</span></span>
</div>
<div class="rc-examples-new">
We've got <span class="hl-s">a lot of</span> apples.<br>
I eat <span class="hl-s">a lot of</span> fruit.<br>
She has <span class="hl-s">a lot of</span> friends.
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="rc-card c-red">
<div class="rc-card-topbar"></div>
<div class="rc-card-body">
<div class="rc-card-label">❌ Verneinter Satz</div>
<div class="rc-card-num">3</div>
<div class="rc-rule">In Verneinungen unterscheidest du nach Nomen-Typ:<br><b>many</b> bei countable · <b>much</b> bei uncountable</div>
<div class="rc-formula">
  <span class="fc fc-neg">don't / doesn't</span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">+</span><span class="fc fc-many">many</span></span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">/</span><span class="fc fc-much">much</span></span>
</div>
<div class="rc-examples-new">
My dad doesn't watch <span class="hl-subj">many</span> films. <span style="font-size:11px;color:#9a7050">(films = countable)</span><br>
I don't like <span class="hl-neg">much</span> sugar in my tea. <span style="font-size:11px;color:#9a7050">(sugar = uncountable)</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="rc-card c-blue">
<div class="rc-card-topbar"></div>
<div class="rc-card-body">
<div class="rc-card-label">❓ Fragen</div>
<div class="rc-card-num">4</div>
<div class="rc-rule">Auch in Fragen: <b>How many</b> bei countable · <b>How much</b> bei uncountable.</div>
<div class="rc-formula">
  <span class="fc fc-wh">How</span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">+</span><span class="fc fc-many">many</span></span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">/</span><span class="fc fc-much">much</span></span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">+</span><span class="fc fc-do">Nomen</span></span>
</div>
<div class="rc-examples-new">
How <span class="hl-subj">many</span> apples do we need?<br>
How <span class="hl-neg">much</span> money do you have?
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="rc-card c-indigo">
<div class="rc-card-topbar"></div>
<div class="rc-card-body">
<div class="rc-card-label">💡 Eselsbrücke</div>
<div class="rc-card-num">5</div>
<div class="rc-rule">Wenn du dir unsicher bist:</div>
<div class="rc-examples-new">
Lassen sich die Nomen <b>zählen</b>,<br>
musst du immer <b>many</b> wählen.<br><br>
Bei <b>uncountable</b> (Stoffe, Begriffe): <b>much</b>.<br>
Im bejahten Satz immer am sichersten: <b>a lot of</b>.
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="rc-card c-teal">
<div class="rc-card-topbar"></div>
<div class="rc-card-body">
<div class="rc-card-label">⚠️ Häufige Fehler</div>
<div class="rc-card-num">6</div>
<div class="rc-examples-new">
❌ I have <b>much</b> friends. → ✅ I have <b>many</b> friends.<br>
❌ How <b>many</b> bread? → ✅ How <b>much</b> bread?<br>
❌ I drink <b>much</b> water every day. → ✅ I drink <b>a lot of</b> water every day.<br>
<span style="font-size:11px;color:#9a7050">(im bejahten Satz besser <b>a lot of</b>)</span>
</div>
</div>
